reviews.review_text: md5s... Good show and good recording, but just 3 stars because the md5s of d1t07 (Bird Song) fail to verify.
Well rounded sound Compared to the other sources from this night, this one has a nice, well rounded sound. After about 30 seconds of listening I really got into it. A solid warm/live sound. Thanks!
